It has been 8 years since I first join irc. There was a time when most of scanlation groups had a channel with many users from different countries. However everything changes now. Even my channel is so boring cause there are only me and some of lurkers. I wonder that if I should close my irc channel and leave this place from now on.

Well, I actually don't like to read novel 'coz I prefer images than letters. Thus 99.99% of my collection is manga. However there are times that I feel boring and there was nothing for me to leech, I wandered with novel XD Man who doesn't take off his clothes vol 1 Man who doesn't take off his clothes vol 1
Even though I haven't received all ordered manga, I can't wait to share XD Last year Now

After 2 weeks with photography, I just realize that there is very long distance between idea and reality. 

I had many idea for a photo shot but I couldn't make it happen  T__T

I take a photography subject in this semester as my elective course so I think from next week, I will have a lot of pic to post. I know from the very beginning that I'm not good at art, but who cares. Moreover just few ppl knew about this lj and me so there is nothing for embarrassing XD
